Package: bgmElicit
Title: Elicit Network Structure Priors for Bayesian Graphical Models Using Large Language Models
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Nikola", "Sekulovski", email = "n.sekulovski@uva.nl", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Meike", "Waaijers", role = "ctb"),
    person("Giuseppe", "Arena", role = "ctb"))
Description: Provides functions for eliciting prior edge inclusion probabilities in Bayesian graphical models (BGMs) using large language models (LLMs). The package allows users to specify variable sets and optional contextual information to query LLMs for conditional associations between variable pairs. It includes both a full and simplified elicitation function. It also provides the option to elicit the parameters for a Beta-Bernoulli ans the Stochastic Block model priors on the network structure.
